<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - (ṭwby̱ lly ạ̹tẖmh ạ̹tgẖfr .. wkẖṭạyạh ạ̹tsrt
 mḥfwẓ mn ạlnạr wạlkẖṭr .. wạldynwnẗ ʿbrt)2
 1- ạ̉ṣbḥ mn ạ̉wlạd ạllh .. lyh fy ạlạbn ḍmạn wḥyạẗ
 (wạlrwḥ ạlqdws jwạh)2 .. byʿrfh kl mạ llh
 2- (ạ̹tḥrr bʿd ạlgẖfrạn .. wạ̹tbrr ʿạysẖ fy ạ̉mạn
 (wạlsẖyṭạn mạlwsẖ slṭạn)2 .. ạ̉ṣlh mn ạ̉wlạd ạllh
 3- (kl mạ llh ạ̉ṣbḥ lyh .. wlạ sẖyʾ mn ạldynwnẗ ʿlyh)2
 (wạlwʿd ạlmḍmwn fy ạ̹ydyh)2 .. mn ạlbryẗ lḥd smạh
 4- (ysqṭ ạ̉ywh lknh fy ywm .. ạlrwḥ yḥzn fyh wylwm)2
 (wyrjʿh frḥạn wyqwm)2 .. ttrdlh bhjth bạllh
 5- (mrḍy ʿnh fy ạlmsyḥ .. mtgẖṭy bdm ạldẖbyḥ)2
 (yḥlạ lh ạlgẖny̱ wạltsbyḥ)2 .. wạltmjyd lạsm ạllh</lyrics>
<title>ṭwby lly</title>
<author>bạsm sẖkry, bạsm sẖkry</author>
